        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Timely Replacement Under Secure and Trusted for Early and Dependable Broadband Networks Act or the TRUSTED Broadband Networks Act </b></p> <p>This bill excludes from specified environmental and historic preservation review a project to permanently remove and replace communications equipment or services that the Federal Communications Commission has determined pose a threat to national security. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
